text: This transmits obsolete IRM 4.49.1, Economist Program, Overview - Economist Program.
The Economist Program as described in this IRM no longer exists. Economists are part of the Economic Practice Network in the Treaty and Transfer Pricing Operations Practice Area.
IRM 4.49.1 dated November 3, 2006 is obsolete as of the date of this transmittal.
